    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Human figures or dolls created to illustrate or promote specific fashions in clothing, textiles, and hair styling; especially popular from the 16th to the 18th century in Europe.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
